to\": 598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Blitzboks suffered an agonising defeat to France in the semi-finals, the SA teambounced back to beat Australia for the bronze medalat the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999716851566, \"rank\": 2.785336487804604e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1020192962085437e-24, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 712, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 2.9817804166872485e-12, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Blitzboks\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"an agonising defeat\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medalat\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosko Specman, who became the first rugby player to earn two medals at the Olympics, said the second meant as much as the first achieved in Rio in 2016.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"score\": 0.9999999993219717, \"rank\": 5.405199483502685e-10, \"text\": \"Rosko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\"}, {\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}, {\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.53651194304812e-12, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first rugby player\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"two medals\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What a journey it has been for me, to earn two medals eight years apart - that is special,\\\" said Specman.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1019, \"end\": 1026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What a journey\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"two medals\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But even more special is the journey we had to get to this point.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the journey\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the dark moments in Harare, where we missed out on qualification, to Monaco, where we used our final chance.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harare\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4014429926888912e-13, \"text\": \"Harare\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harare\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harare\"}, {\"begin\": 1170, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.7569070350402994, \"rank\": 0.3211606086380602, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dark moments\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"qualification\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"our final chance\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We may have been the last team in, but we are bronze medallists.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last team\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze medallists\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well done to the coaches and management who got this group to believe it is possible.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"management\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"this group\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And on a personal note, I would like to thank God who gave me this chance to earn a second medal in the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a personal note\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"this chance\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"a second medal\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Philip Snyman, a member of the 2016 squad that won a medal in the inaugural Rugby Sevens event, achieving a second - this time as coach - said it was more important that the credit should go to the players who made it possible, rather than his own achievement.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philip Snyman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.9915502502023255e-13, \"text\": \"Rugby Sevens\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 squad\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"the credit\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"his own achievement\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a great management, and this win was also for those back in South Africa, but the moment belongs to the players - I am so proud of them and what they achieved here today,\\\" said Snyman.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1810, \"end\": 1822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.9999991080362064, \"rank\": 7.786787877235028e-07, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great management\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"this win\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"Snyman\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had our ups and downs, especially on the first day, but the way the team came back on the next two competition days made me so proud.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our ups\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"downs\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"the first day\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the next two competition days\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had our lapses and could have been in the final, but all that matters will be the bronze medals they earned today.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our lapses\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medals\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is so deserved to a group of guys who never stopped working and playing for their country.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"guys\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\"